reviewText: We love this.  My 4 year old is learning how to read and this is so awesome.  I wish they spelled the words out loud instead of just showing on the screen but the songs are catchy and my 4 year old can recognize the words outside of watching the video.  Even my 3 year old is getting into it.
This is a great video to help children learn sight words.  My grandchildren listen and sing along with it over and over.
This is the EXACT same thing as level 1 sight words. Don't buy both!
